title: Did Joe Biden publicly reveal the identity of the special unit that killed Bin Laden?
subtitle: In the question are the statements made by the former Vice-President of the United States following the raid that killed the mastermind of the 9/11 attacks in the United States.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Vice-President Joe Biden then publicly identified the special operations unit responsible for the killing of Osama bin Laden during a speech on 3 May 2011 at the Atlantic Council Awards dinner.
